MARCFieldLabel: LOCATION OF OTHER ARCHIVAL MATERIALS NOTE (R)
Justification for Mapping: Did not combine with $c because both subfields are repeatable and could result in names for two or more places being associated with one rda:Place entity. CEY 2023-02-23
Transformation Notes: Mint Place entity related by "location of collection" to manifestation being described. Use value as unstructured value of name of place http://rdaregistry.info/Elements/p/P70001. Mint a new place for each occurrence of subfield.

Mint nomen related to newly-minted manifestation using http://rdaregistry.info/Elements/m/P30134 title of manifestation, and record value of $d as nomen string for that Nomen entity. Mint item entity related to newly-minted manifestation using http://rdaregistry.info/Elements/m/P30103. Also mint corresponding collection expression and work and relate to one another? CEY 2023-02-01
